<h1 align="center">About</h1>

<div>
<p>
Beijing's air quality isn't great.  The omnipresent haze gives the impressision that there's only one level: "<a href="http://www.guardian.co.uk/environment/blog/2010/nov/19/crazy-bad-beijing-air-pollution">crazy bad</a>."   But there are some good days, some that really are "<a href="http://www.chinadialogue.net/article/show/single/en/4134-Beijing-s-blue-sky-diary">blue sky days</a>."<br>
</p>

<p>To all the Beijingers, I hope this tool helps.<br></p>

<p>To all the schadenfrued-obsessed voyeurs, I hope this shows that it's not all the bad.<br></p>
</div>

